'''天主教拉菲亞教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Lafiensis}}）是[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教阿布賈總教區|阿布賈總教區]]。

教區於2000年12月5日成立<ref>{{cite web |title=LAFIENSIS* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_20001205_petitum-est.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-01-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106180259/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_20001205_petitum-est.html |archivedate=2020-01-06 |language=la |date=2000-12-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，位於[[納薩拉瓦州|納薩拉瓦州]]；2004年時有教友189,686人（佔轄區人口10.2%）、十五個堂區和卅四名司鐸。教區主教現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 06.01.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2020/01/06/0011/00015.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-01-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106151156/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2020/01/06/0011/00015.html |archivedate=2020-01-06 |language=it |date=2020-01-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

